{"article_id":"nTKwje3U5kngmE30","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Good morning and welcome to Fox News First .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Here 's what you need to know","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"as you start your day ...","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Atlanta police shooting autopsy reveals","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Rayshard Brooks suffered 2 gunshot wounds to the back ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"death ruled homicide","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"As the killing of a 27-year-old black man in an encounter with two white officers late Friday rekindled fiery protests in Atlanta","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"and prompted the police chief ' s resignation ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"the medical examiner on Sunday found","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Rayshard Brooks suffered two gunshot wounds to the back","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and his death has been ruled a homicide .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The office of Fulton County Medical Examiner performed an autopsy on Brooks on Sunday","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that the gunshot wounds to the back created organ failure","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"because of blood loss .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"One minute , Brooks appeared to be chatting cooperatively with Atlanta police ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"he ' d had a couple of drinks","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"to celebrate his daughter ' s birthday","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"and agreeing to a breath test .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"The next , they were wrestling on the ground","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and grappling over a Taser","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"before Brooks took the weapon","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and pointed it at the officers .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Seconds later , three gunshots sounded","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and Brooks fell to the ground .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Atlanta police video released Sunday","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"showing a seemingly routine sobriety check outside a Wendy ' s restaurant","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that quickly spun out of control ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"ending in gunfire .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Police said Sunday","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"the department terminated Officer Garrett Rolfe ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"who fired the fatal shots ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and Officer Devin Brosnan was placed on administrative duty .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Rolfe had worked for the department since October 2013 ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"and Brosnan since September 2018 .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Click here for more on our top story .","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"- Atlanta police shooting 'completely different ' than Floyd death ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"says CBP chief :","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"'He took their weapon '","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"- Dan Bongino on how Atlanta officers handled Rayshard Brooks case","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"- George Floyd 's brother tells police :","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"'You can do your job","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and still maintain respect for others '","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"China locks down 10 more neighborhoods ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"fires officials amid coronavirus resurgence :","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"reports","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"At least 10 residential communities near the Yuquandong market in Beijing 's Haidian District placed under lockdown","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"after `` multiple cases '' were found over the weekend .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Residents were ordered to go under home quarantine and take nucleic acid tests for the virus .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"All of the infections reportedly had ties to the Xinfadi market in Beijing ' s southern Fengtai district","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"-- identified as the center of a new cluster of cases .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Click here for more .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"- Surgeon General Jerome